  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0d9c\u0dc3\u0dca-\u0d9a\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf-\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca-\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dcf-\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dad\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0d9a\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1-\u0dc4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dcf/101-617022",
  "time_ut": 1658754556,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dad\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The tree cutter tried to cut the fuel station owner's son with a saw",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Deyandara police said that a tree cutter who threatened to cut and injure the son of the owner of the Deyandara petrol station by cutting and injuring him with a chainsaw was arrested for questioning on suspicion that he did not release the fuel required for the chainsaw machine.",
        "At the time of trying to get fuel by bringing a motorcycle that does not belong to the number category related to the date, the staff of the filling station did not allow it.",
        "Later he went home and brought the chainsaw and asked for fuel.",
        "After an argument, the suspect tried to cut the son of the owner of the filling station who had argued with him by using a chain saw.",
        "However, the people around that time and the police prevented it.",
        "Accordingly, the 40-year-old suspect, a resident of Deiendara Danhena, who was arrested along with the chainsaw machine, was to be presented to the court."
      ],
